div.style: color: rgb(114, 28, 36) !important; display: table; white-space: break-spaces; line-height: 1.5; max-width: 200px; text-align: center; width: 200px;

span.p:
500 Internal Server Error
Generic crash.
Code bug or unhandled exception.

div.style: color: rgb(114, 28, 36) !important; display: table-cell; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.5; max-width: 200px; text-align: center;

span.p:
502 Bad Gateway
Upstream error.
Proxy received garbage.

div.style: color: rgb(114, 28, 36) !important; display: table-cell; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.5; max-width: 200px; text-align: center;

span.p:
503 Service Unavailable
Server is down/busy.
Maintenance or overload.

div.style: color: rgb(114, 28, 36) !important; display: table-cell; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.5; max-width: 200px; text-align: center;

span.p:
504 Gateway Timeout
Too slow.
Database or API took too long.

div.style: color: rgb(133, 100, 4) !important; display: table-cell; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.5; max-width: 200px; text-align: center;

span.p:
400 Bad Request
Generic error.
Invalid syntax or bad JSON.

div.style: color: rgb(133, 100, 4) !important; display: table-cell; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.5; max-width: 200px; text-align: center;

span.p:
401 Unauthorized
Who are you?
Log in required (Missing Token).

div.style: color: rgb(133, 100, 4) !important; display: table-cell; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.5; max-width: 200px; text-align: center;

span.p:
403 Forbidden
I know you, but NO.
Valid login, but no permission.

div.style: color: rgb(133, 100, 4) !important; display: table-cell; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.5; max-width: 200px; text-align: center;

span.p:
404 Not Found
It's not here.
Wrong URL or ID invalid.

div.style: color: rgb(133, 100, 4) !important; display: table-cell; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.5; max-width: 200px; text-align: center;

span.p:
429 Too Many Requests
Calm down.
Rate limit exceeded.

div.style: color: rgb(0, 64, 133) !important; display: table; white-space: break-spaces; line-height: 1.5; max-width: 200px; text-align: center; width: 200px;

span.p:
301 Moved Permanently
New URL is permanent.
Browser remembers (caches) this.

div.style: color: rgb(0, 64, 133) !important; display: table-cell; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.5; max-width: 200px; text-align: center;

span.p:
302 Found (Temporary)
New URL is temporary.
Do not cache heavily.

div.style: color: rgb(0, 64, 133) !important; display: table; white-space: break-spaces; line-height: 1.5; max-width: 200px; text-align: center; width: 200px;

span.p:
304 Not Modified
Resource hasn't changed.
Use your local cache (Save data).

div.style: color: rgb(21, 87, 36) !important; display: table; white-space: break-spaces; line-height: 1.5; max-width: 200px; text-align: center; width: 200px;

span.p:
200 OK
Standard success.
Data fetched or updated successfully.

div.style: color: rgb(21, 87, 36) !important; display: table-cell; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.5; max-width: 200px; text-align: center;

span.p:
201 Created
New resource created.
Result of a POST request.

div.style: color: rgb(21, 87, 36) !important; display: table; white-space: break-spaces; line-height: 1.5; max-width: 200px; text-align: center; width: 200px;

span.p:
204 No Content
Action successful, but empty response.
Common in DELETE.

div.style: color: black !important; display: table-cell; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.5; max-width: 200px; text-align: center;

span.p:
üë§ Client / User
Initiates HTTP Request
(Browser, App, API Client)

span.p:
